50|$|Ozidi is a folk hero {{among the}} Ijo of Nigeria, {{and the subject}} of <b>The</b> Ozidi <b>Saga</b> {{composed}} by playwright and poet John Pepper Clark. <b>The</b> <b>saga's</b> first performance was in 1966.|$|R
